data.description: Price Improvement!! Amazing opportunity to own this beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath town home located only a few miles from the Beach!  This beautiful home offers a spacious kitchen and dining area along with a screened lanai overlooking the preserve.  Laundry room has a newer washer and dryer and is located upstairs on bedroom level for convenience.  The master suite features a soaking tub, walk-in shower, double vanities, and 2 large walk-in closets.  Additional 2 guest bedrooms are also located on the upper level.  This fantastic property has an affordable HOA fee which includes a beautiful community pool and monitored gate.  Whether you are looking for a year round use or seasonal home, you cannot beat the location of this amazing community. With close proximity to beaches, shopping, restaurants, airport etc.  New AC in 2020, newer appliances, carpet and interior paint as well.
